Tu jahan.. reh chuka hai
Mai wahaan.. Ja chuka hoon
Tu jahan.. reh chuka hai
Mere dil main kahin tu chupa toh nahi
Muskurata hua tu yahin hai kahin
Dhoondta phir raha ek nishani teri
Mil bhi jaye tu poochu kahaani meri
Kis liye kis liye jee raha hoon yahaan
❤❤❤❤

snippet.textDisplay:
Anupam, you created a magic...of music.

Very soothing for MON....gud hindi - bangla mix and gud mix of singers ..
All 3 have their style and you used it beautifully .
Music piece before last stanza is gud western one followed by Satyaki and your voice.
You are a CREATOR and so  create to soothe Humanity.
